node.text:
For over 70 years, we have made it our mission to be the most trusted choice for a bride searching for her dream wedding dress 👰 From the moment you walk through our infamous glass doors, your experience with us is unlike anywhere else 🌎⁣
⁣
You’ll be greeted by our friendly staff, welcomed into our 35,000 square foot main salon, and paired with your knowledgeable bridal consultant ✨⁣You will also have access to the largest curated selection of wedding dresses in the country and a devoted staff of over 200 to help you every step of the way 🙌 ⁣
⁣
Ready to experience the magic of #Kleinfeld yourself? Tap the link in bio to book an appointment 💗

“When I first saw my wife in her #Kleinfeld dress, I thought to myself, ‘My goodness I am the luckiest person alive!’ 😍 @AngelinaGeftos looked like an absolute dream come true and I can’t believe how beautiful her @EssenseOfAustralia dress was,” says @ThoringtonCourtney. ✨

As a longtime fan of @SayYes_TLC, it was “a dream come true” for Angelina to come to Kleinfeld to shop for her perfect wedding day look. 👰‍♀️“I saw Kleinfeld posted on Instagram for a trunk show. I brought it up to my best friends and we booked the flights and went! ✈️ As a plus size bride, it felt hard to wedding dress shop because no one had a large selection of samples in my size. But once I arrived to Kleinfeld, I was in awe‼️ It’s better than I imagined from the show,” says Angelina. 📺 

All of a sudden, I saw @LisaSYTTD and felt overwhelmed (with excitement!) because her and @RandyFenoli are my favorites from the show. I thought for sure she was going to grab someone else, but then she came straight over to me — I was in pure shock! 😱 Lisa was so kind and made me feel right at home.” 🏡
